{"tid":525614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逼6歲女口愛　小提琴師逞慾！親妹妹也受害","createTime":"2018-01-11T00:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T03:19:29.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5e74d7003a75da29dc1030ec07f80edd7c5024f1","tid":525614,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T00:10:52.000Z","msg":"不僅對年幼妹妹逞慾，12年後以小提琴師身分，也對年僅6歲的女學生性侵，造成被害者難以抹煞的陰影。<br />\n今日出版的《自由時報》報導，該名小提琴教師還未當上老師之前，2000年在家強迫6歲的妹妹口交，2004年間強行伸進衣褲摸揉胸部與下體，幾個月後又強行抓住妹妹手臂握住自己的下體手淫。<br />\n<br />\n他成為小提琴教師後，2012年間在工作室內強脫6歲女學生內褲性侵得逞，隔年再度逞慾一次，甚至開車載著她到郊區，在車上要求口交得逞。直到去年被害女學生才向母親訴苦，「那回憶有夠慘、超噁心的」。其親妹也指控，直到高中2年級仍有遭性侵的陰影，到校接受輔導且曾向親人吐露過此事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180111/1276308\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180111%2F1276308&d=rAtfao6yB4dxNkpNzqY3kP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=3eeea0bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180111%2F1276308&h=f14d4dd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180111/1276308</a><br />\n估計住新北"},{"pid":"6e77b9b899a56f06481bdd563d1bcdbb3ed3c375","tid":525614,"uid":48905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T00:43:42.000Z","msg":"施旖婕？"},{"pid":"b41da4769d50d7170bd538b634473c02efb3ca73","tid":525614,"uid":5006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T00:44:40.000Z","msg":"屌 又要準備睇潮文"},{"pid":"4f75b74e08721cb3dbf2a5f306fa6e49490a02a5","tid":525614,"uid":4517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T01:51:57.000Z","msg":"所以話..."},{"pid":"b0e03de0415fd5bbb67ead1898dace89d420b643","tid":525614,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T03:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3o7528RQ7YTVkLSywU/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fme